company.name: Union Beverage Packers
company.description:
Union Beverage’s strategic aim is to be a World-class hot-fill manufacturer.  Union has provided Customers with innovative ideas to deliver products in a cost-effective manner. Union is currently implementing projects to reduce its carbon footprint.   Union’s focus is to produce in the most efficient way possible. 

Our Company's Mission: 
     -To exceed our customers expectations in quality, delivery, and cost through 
       continuous improvement.
     -To support our customers by providing products and services of exceptional 
       value which help them gain competitive advantage in their markets.
     -To expand opportunities for development and career growth for our 
       employees.
     -To operate Our Company on a sustainable financial basis of profitable 
       growth, increasing value for our shareholders without compromising our 
       customers, employees and community.

Company's History: 
   -  Union Beverage First Production
            November 2003 built first Line 
     - Through the Years Grew to a 3-Shift Operation
     - Second Hot Fill Line was installed and commissioned in March, 2006
     - In July 2008, Third Hot Filler and Thermal System were installed
     - In June 2012, Can Fill Line & multiservice line was installed
     - Plant Capability
             To Fill PET, Glass, HDPE, Cans
             Large & Small Batches
      -2019: Entered into an agreement with Mark Anthony Brewing to manage the 
       packaging portion of White Claw for Mark Anthony. The facility is located at 
       Union Beverage’s facility at 600 N. Union Ave., Hillside NJ.
